// A PLURAL interface-of-weak shadow return (`[IWeakPage]`, sole implementor the
// @weak model `WeakPage`) is STILL a hard error (this must not open the
// plural gate). The plural gate in shadow_transform runs before the inline
// classification and rejects with ShadowResolverPluralUnsupported regardless of
// whether the (singular) member would otherwise route to the inline weak arm.
//- UserWeakPages.js
/**
 * @relayField User.weak_pages: [IWeakPage]
 * @rootFragment UserWeakPagesResolverFragment
 * @returnFragment UserWeakPagesReturnFragment
 */
graphql`fragment UserWeakPagesResolverFragment on User {
  page {
    ...UserWeakPagesReturnFragment
  }
}`

